lead_paragraph: Mariya Moore sank five 3-pointers and scored 26 points on Sunday to lead No. 14 Louisville to a 78-54 win over Wake Forest and remain unbeaten in Atlantic Coast Conference play this season.

headline.print_headline: No. 14 Louisville Women Beat Wake Forest 78-54
